file-utils provides header-only filesystem utilities.

Usage:
    find_package(file-utils CONFIG REQUIRED)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE file-utils::file-utils)

Example:
    #include <file-utils/file_utils.hpp>
    auto content = file::read_all("config.json");
    file::write_all("output.txt", "hello");
    auto files = file::list_files("./src");
